OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FShane MacGowan's wife hopes
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Ffor Christmas hit          
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The wife of late Pogues frontman Shane 
OL,6, MacGowan has said she hopes his song   
OL,7, Fairytale of New York will be Christmas
OL,8, number one in his memory.              
OL,10,FVictoria Mary Clarke told BBC Radio 4's
OL,11,FToday programme she was "very much in  
OL,12,Ffavour" of the track, which also       
OL,13,Ffeatures Kirsty MacColl, reaching the  
OL,14,Ftop spot.                              
OL,16,F"It would be nice, wouldn't it?" she   
OL,17,Fsaid. "It should be the Christmas      
OL,18,Fnumber one. It absolutely should."     
OL,20,FMacGowan, 65, died on Thursday,        
OL,21,Ffollowing a long battle with illness.  
